title: Ancient Cedars Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, Take-out, Canadian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. The menu was created out of compromise between the two partners, one vegan and one omnivore, so it's 50% vegan food choices and 50% non vegan. Features breakfast food, smoothies plus lunch sandwiches and burgers with seasonal specials. Located on a golf course. Has Wi-Fi.
